type: text/markdown

with `pwgen`

``` bash
pwgen -s -y 64 1
```

``` example
YA1rD_P(d6AIMg'tX"[fz&Jj$k:9*c1-?!L]%pF%ED)\4R\iQ;~qe[A$i([*f[SG
```

without external tools

``` bash
tr -dc 'a-zA-Z0-9' </dev/urandom | head -c 64
```

``` example
RF7zE5nwflWDU7RbUrOnSr7hZj4DZlNrdM4va0rkxxaPJ7n3wr40nkKaP1atE03J
```
